***
Some devices may show that Audio may not be found or MACs may show error regarding pyaudio

1) For that please run this following code line:
  !apt install libasound2-dev portaudio19-dev libportaudio2 libportaudiocpp0 ffmpeg

2) Run the following code if Tkinter doesn't work:  
  !apt install ghostscript python3-tk

3) Run the following for google colab or if some programs show that there is no environment for the gui:
  ### CREATE VIRTUAL DISPLAY ###
  !apt-get install -y xvfb # Install X Virtual Frame Buffer
  import os
  os.system('Xvfb :1 -screen 0 1600x1200x16  &')    # create virtual display with size 1600x1200 and 16 bit color. Color can be changed to 24 or 8
  os.environ['DISPLAY']=':1.0'    # tell X clients to use our virtual DISPLAY :1.0.

